PATCHES PROPOSED TO BACKPORT FROM TRUNK:
  [ New proposals should be added at the end of the list ]

  * core: Various memory leaks and uninitialized values.
    Trunk patch: http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=revision&revision=1133639
    Jira: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TS-828
    +1: zwoop, zym

  * build: remove uninstall target from build system
    Trunk patch: http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1136958&view=rev
    Jira: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TS-842
    +1: igalic, zwoop

  * API: TSHttpTxnErrorBodySet() can leak memory.
    Trunk patch: http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1137775&view=rev
    Jira: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TS-826
    +1: zwoop, zym

  * Build: build fails with --as-needed --no-copy-dt-needed-entries
    Trunk patch: http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1142523&view=rev
    Jira: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TS-868
    +1: igalic, zwoop

  * HTTP: Built in error for host not found looks like Internet Explorer
          error.
    Trunk patch: http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1143116&view=rev
    Jira: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TS-860
    +1: zwoop

